<p>
<note n="0594008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0594008">金剛藏…十一 vajragarbhābhisaṁbodhi-nāma-kalpa-rājāḥ.</note>
<note n="0594009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0594009">samāhita.</note>
<note n="0594010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0594010">kurukllā.</note>
<note n="0594011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0594011">hrīḥ.</note>
<note n="0594012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0594012">asura.</note>
<note n="0594013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0594013">Oṁ vajrapuṣpe āḥ hūṁ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0594014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0594014">Oṁ vajradhūpe(?) āḥ hūṁ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0595001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595001">Oṁ vajra dīpe āḥ hūṁ svāha.</note>
<note n="0595002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595002">Oṁ vajra gandhe āh hūṁ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0595003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595003">Oṁ vajra naivedya āḥ hūṁ svāhā.</note>
<note n="0595004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595004">火天歡喜真言 agni-saṁtoṣa-mantra.</note>
<note n="0595005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595005">Oṁ agnaye mahā(te)jaḥ sarvakāma prasādhakaḥ kārūnya kṛta satvārthaḥ asminasannīhitobhava, agnyā vāha naṁ, tvaṁ devisāk ṣi bhūtāsi he vajra krodha pūjite, nānatna dharī dhātri amuke, haṁ maṇḍalaṁ likhimitvātha cevaparārtha ca sādhitu gaccha havyabhuka, āgamiṣyāmi yathā kāle sarva siddhi kuru ṣvame.</note>
<note n="0595006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595006">獻閼…言 argha-mantra.</note>
<note n="0595007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595007">Oṁ jaḥ hūṁ vaṁ hoḥ khaṁ raṁ.</note>
<note n="0595008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595008">淨水真言 pāya-mantra.</note>
<note n="0595009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595009">Oṁ rī rī hūṁ khaḥ.</note>
<note n="0595010" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595010">獻食真言 naivedya-mantra.</note>
<note n="0595011" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595011">Oṁ thaṁ thaṁ.</note>
<note n="0595012" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595012">（熾盛…二）＝hevajre ḍākīnījāla saṁvare dvitīya kalpasya prathamaḥ paṭālaḥ.</note>
<note n="0595013" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595013">yoginī.</note>
<note n="0595014" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0595014">悉囉訶 sihlaka(silhaka) 梵本寫誤多不堪揭正確梵註，下略</note>
</p>
